{"tid":161420,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果女朋友煮野好難食","createTime":"2017-03-18T13:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T14:31:07.000Z","uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b12cf61a839993aa91ff46699d69b1a841d1ca","tid":161420,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"今日我親手下廚俾男朋友食，佢6點個陣已經叫餓，咁我就拿拿臨去煮。其實個飯都係我第一次煮，上網睇食譜跟住，點知我落少左水搞到成煲飯一半熟一半生米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我就倒水落去再煲，點知搞左個幾兩個鐘都救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />男朋友已經餓到咕咕聲<br />\n<br />\n最後真係整得好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難食到食唔落咁濟，本身我係想試住燴飯 點知變到爛容容，好似bb食個啲糊仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係你女朋友 你地心入面會唔會好唔鐘意？我好內疚 要男朋友餓咁耐 最後俾屎佢食咁 我地食個陣我仲有少少想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f248e845461141e77ddd36514a4a82fc54602cd","tid":161420,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"幫佢含下就冇野"},{"pid":"331105eb22c67f70bbd052437522625e83ca7338","tid":161420,"uid":89155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"肯煮好好啦 個個人都會有新手唔識既時候。但起碼肯煮先。懶先冇得救。加油"},{"pid":"5a1ba39c50a765fc876629c48b9422f1c45b1a31","tid":161420,"uid":60739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"唔會啊，雖然我女朋友煮嘢好好味，但只要你有心就得啦"},{"pid":"a54899e5cf78e7331989aaf34168e2b1b6c5c6c8","tid":161420,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"我會煮番比佢食"},{"pid":"d9836006d9a363e78de0dcf16a48186a11e5b978","tid":161420,"uid":25364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"煮得出黎都會食既<br />\n但我從來唔會叫女朋友煮野俾我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732278f904690385c9b22aa348613d8cccf90ba0","tid":161420,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/110100_0a543d26ca0fa28a17fdfc3e2c461ba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F110100_0a543d26ca0fa28a17fdfc3e2c461ba1.jpg&h=3e61fa83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你問吓馮老蛋巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4195465b19d11ca7eee55c97ad80f2d06c9938","tid":161420,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"未我煮屌你"},{"pid":"d3a7cbd4b88da29128748602cc25bb24f85ff59e","tid":161420,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aa2a415a8d52726e3554cd51aeed08b8ff454b0","tid":161420,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你識煮先好煮啦好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係你面前更係話無所謂架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煮舊屎仲要讚舊屎好食</blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf57a90fb9b50d33a19da0d1b6f6e8cef418840","tid":161420,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"女仔點都要識野食 唔洗好味 首先要正確煮熟啲飯先"},{"pid":"d0a61f53004de6845e3e5e3f1742360a776dd6b2","tid":161420,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"自己煮多d先上去煮啦<br />\n趕時間就食外賣啦"},{"pid":"4ad600ac91c7482c1638408fff3aa42b3bb8beeb","tid":161420,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女仔點都要識野食 唔洗好味 首先要正確煮熟啲飯先</blockquote><br />\n我平時係煮開飯的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但個食譜教落半杯水 我跟足 屌 咁就死左 <br />\n其實唔係飯唔熟應該會好食，我岩岩煮個陣男朋友仲話好香 點知死左個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0860c6c799857423ebe8f72dba161a28e62be65","tid":161420,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己煮多d先上去煮啦<br />\n趕時間就食外賣啦</blockquote><br />\n我自己住 日日自己煮飯食，但今次真係失晒手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}